title: All-new 'Win Wess' Toaster!'
itunes:title: All-new 'Win Wess' Toaster!'
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- discuss the latest NFL news and react to the latest "Top 100" rankings. Then, Chris Wesseling takes on contestants in "Win Wess' Toaster!" -- an NFL trivia-based game of skill and valor (18:12).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
